                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" htag="li" hclass="sense" id="americanmedicalassociation_sng_1"><span class="sensetop" htag="span" hclass="sensetop"><span class="def" hclass="def" htag="span">the largest professional organization for US doctors. It began in 1847 and has its main office in <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/chicago" title="Chicago definition"><span class="ndv">Chicago</span></a>. The <span class="dh">AMA</span> supports high standards in medical education, research and work, and it has great political influence.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
